-34" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$fan-fu-min-34'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-d768007379f6fc8276c2efe3f41b6e64_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="樊富珉"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/jingshenjiankang/fan-fu-min-34/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/fan-fu-min-34" data-hovercard='p$t$fan-fu-min-34'>樊富珉</a><div class="bio">清华大学心理学系教授</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/wang-gang-9-8-47" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-gang-9-8-47'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f55fb894bd47d95db8f3cf5f7d06e5e4_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="王刚"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/jingshenjiankang/wang-gang-9-8-47/answers" class="answers text-muted">3 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/wang-gang-9-8-47" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-gang-9-8-47'>王刚</a><div class="bio">首都医科大学附属北京安定医院 <span class="bull">&bull;</span> 博士学位，主任医师，教授，博士生导师，抑郁症治疗中心主任</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/jweir28" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$jweir28'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-ebcf37b5252ab6ed2982d5d57e9ad032_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="魏镜"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/jingshenjiankang/jweir28/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/jweir28" data-hovercard='p$t$jweir28'>魏镜</a><div class="bio">北京协和医院，心理医学科</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/wang-xiang-63-1" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-xiang-63-1'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-1de1e21d604de201473bd5e08fec6662_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="王向群"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/jingshenjiankang/wang-xiang-63-1/answers" class="answers text-muted">3 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/wang-xiang-63-1" data-hoverca